Southampton's World Cup star Luke Shaw said he was ‘gutted’ on Tuesday night after two of the club’s highly rated Under 18 coaches were fired.

Les Reed, who is now executive director at  St Mary’s, approved the decision to sack former Southampton players Jason Dodd and Paul Williams as part of his battle for control of the club’s academy.

